cross: Paphiopedilum President Fred x Paphiopedilum Magically Wood

measurements.description: One stately flat full flower on one sturdy 25.5-cm inflorescence; dorsal sepal white, veined green-brown, overlaid green basal half, transitioning to light burgundy on marginal two-thirds; synsepal green, burgundy stripes; petals green basal half transitioning to medium burgundy marginally, heavy dark mahogany warts, upper margin hirsute; pouch burgundy, veined darker burgundy; staminode pale green, darker green centrally; substance medium; texture waxy.
